{
  "text": "All of these models are pretrained VGGFace [CITATION_1] models (pretrained ResNet50 on the VGGFace dataset), hence we use a low learning rate of 1e \u2212 4 with batch size of 32 for fine-tuning. Training is done on a randomly generated split of training and validation set [CITATION_2] of images from our dataset of Mary and Gabriel.",
